Class AtomicAction

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nlm.meme.action.LoggedAction.Default
      gov.nih.nlm.meme.action.AtomicAction
All Implemented Interfaces:
LoggedAction
Direct Known Subclasses:
AtomicAction, AtomicChangeAtomAction, AtomicChangeConceptAction, AtomicChangeFieldAction, AtomicChangeReleasabilityAction, AtomicChangeStatusAction, AtomicDeleteAction, AtomicInsertAction
public class AtomicAction
extends LoggedAction.Default

This class generically represents an atomic action, which is typically part of a MolecularAction. This class is associated with the atomic_actions table in the MID.

Author:
MEME Group
